		{
			dependencies: ["3C48F0B4F29CF0A8"]
			description: [
				"&6&lADJ&r is all about creating! This its the third and final time I am saying this."
				""
				"You lose hunger way slower in &6&lADJ&r, as it is kind of a secondary mechanic made to be FUN rather than ANNOYING to constantly maintain. I mean of course you still have to eat something once every few minutes, but it is still far less annoying than in the base game."
				""
				"Cook something funny, I believe in you."
			]
