		{
			dependencies: ["74019EFD0ED8F657"]
			description: [
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_1.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"1. Start by digging a 3x3 hole."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_2.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"2. Place your Water Wheel sideways and pour down your &9Water&r. "
				"Add a singular block to make it flow in one direction. If the wheel is spinning, you did it well. "
				"Place a &7Shaft&r upwards from the Water Wheel."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_3.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"3. Cover everything with any block (Glass was used here in place of Dirt for clarity) and place down the &6Mechanical Bearing&r on top of the &7Shaft&r."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_4.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"4. Add &9Water&r and till the area around the farm in a circle like shown above."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_5.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"5. Place &6Linear Chasis&r in a line like this from the center."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_6.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"6. Add &7Mechanical Harvesters&r to the 4 most outer &6Chasis&r blocks."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_7.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"7. Add Chests."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_8.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"8. &aGlue&r the Chests to the rest of the contraption. You can easily do this by right-clicking one end of the Chasis first with &aSuper Glue&r, and then right-click the outer Chest."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_9.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"9. Right-click the &6Mechanical Bearing&r with an empty hand to update the contraption and make it move."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"{image:adj:textures/other/farm_tutorial_10.png width:100 height:100 align:center}"
				"10. Finally, add plant any crop you want! Harvesters will automatically replant them when harvested."
			]
